snippet.title: Suicide Squad: Kill the Justice League | Season 2 - Meet Mrs. Freeze
snippet.description:
A multiversal cold front has hit Metropolis and it’s not alone. Mrs. Freeze has joined the Suicide Squad to ice Brainiac and save the Flash?! Check out the Season 2 Free* Content Update!

*Base Game required!

Buy now: https://go.wbgames.com/AvailableNow 
 
Suicide Squad: Kill the Justice League is available now on PS5, Xbox Series X|S, and PC.
 
Learn more: https://www.suicidesquadgame.com/en-us
